data.title: Atomic Catering
data.meta_description: Locally owned & operated cafe, we pride ourselves on providing fresh, innovative food & exceptional service, in a fun environment. Located inside Questacon, Australia's National Science and Technology Centre.
data.text:
Are you looking for someone to cater your next event? Large or small, we do it all. Our Catering and Events team have the expertise to ensure your event is a success. Get in touch to start planning the perfect meal for a business lunch, cocktail party, and more!

Atomic Catering offers packages for breakfast, lunch and light refreshments. We also offer dinner for those attending Questacon's Q by Night sessions or school excursion groups visiting Canberra. Let us take care of everything from setup, serving and cleaning

Atomic Catering understands the significance of reducing the impact on the environment that running our caf√© may have. We are committed to sound and innovative environmental practices. Atomic Catering has developed an Environmental Management Plan which outlines our commitment to protecting the environment. If you have any concerns or feedback in relation to our environmental practices please get in touch with us below.
